parseNextItem

public I parseNextItem()
                throws java.io.IOException
Description copied from class: AbstractJsonFeedParser
Parse the next item in the feed and return a new parsed instanceof of the item class. If there is no item to parse, it will return null and automatically close the parser (in which case there is no need to call AbstractJsonFeedParser.close().
